il Young</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">Stevie Wonder</a>等众多娱乐界人物最近也纷纷为哈里斯代言。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-speaks-at-kamala-harris-rally-hits-out-at-donald-trumps-comments-about-detroit-3804404">利佐在卡马拉·哈里斯集会上发表讲话，抨击唐纳德·特朗普关于底特律的言论</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
