inneas-and-billie-eilish-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/finneas-and-billie-eilish-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/finneas-and-billie-eilish-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/finneas-and-billie-eilish-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">芬尼斯 (Finneas)</a>联手在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>节目中演出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Billie Eilish – 《Hit Me Hard and Soft》评论：大胆、精彩、更明亮</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天晚上（10 月 19 日），艾利什第四次以音乐嘉宾身份出现在节目中，她与她的兄弟和长期合作者一起表演了她的第三张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Hit Me Hard and Soft</a> 》中的两首歌曲。</p><p>在此之前，她最近一次出现在《周六夜现场》中是在去年 12 月，当时她在该节目的圣诞节节目中演唱了“祝自己圣诞快乐”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比</em></a>歌谣“What Was I Made For”。</p><p>她以《物以类聚》开场，在简单的蓝天背景下表演。 《Wildflower》采用了更加简约的布景设计，Eilish 在深蓝色灯光下演唱 - 请观看下面的片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Billie Eilish: BIRDS OF A FEATHER (Live) - SNL" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/00OcH_Ktc4U?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Billie Eilish: WILDFLOWER (Live) - SNL" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BRB2umnWTl8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Eilish 目前正在进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">她的“Hit Me Hard And Soft”世界巡回演唱会</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-debut-hit-me-hard-and-soft-tracks-and-rock-through-happier-than-ever-as-she-kicks-off-world-tour-in-quebec-setlist-3798632">北美站</a>，此前她曾向歌迷保证，她的独唱并不是与 Finneas 合作的“结束”。</p><p>然而，这次长途跋涉标志着她第一次在没有她的合著者和制作人的情况下进行演出—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-for-cryin-out-loud-2025-uk-european-and-australian-tour-buy-tickets-3798210">她正在巡回演出以支持他的第二张个人专辑</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-second-album-for-cryin-out-loud-with-hopeful-title-track-3782171">《For Cryin&#39; Out Loud!》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-is-learning-to-do-home-production-without-finneas-3797325">芬尼斯最近还透露，艾利什正在学习“在没有他的情况下进行家庭制作”</a> ，并说“她非常擅长”。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-10-10/billie-eilish-finneas-hit-me-hard-and-soft-grammys-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《洛杉矶时报》</em></a>的一次新采访中，有人指出芬尼斯将“在日程允许的情况下”与他的妹妹一起登上舞台，并于上周在新泽西州纽瓦克的演出中与艾利什一起演奏了“比以往更快乐”（10 月 9 日） ）。</p><p>当该出版物询问是否应该从芬尼斯的缺席得出任何结论时，艾利什回答说：“这实际上并不是任何事情的结束。你不能同时出现在两个地方。”</p><p>艾利什<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-and-finneas-have-never-ever-ever-loved-something-more-than-new-album-hit-me-hard-and-soft-3757252">此前曾公开表示，她和芬尼斯“从未、从未、从未如此热爱过她的最新唱片”</a> ，并补充道：“我们希望你们非常喜欢它，我们会在另一边见到你们的。”</p><p>这位歌手将于明年夏天前往英国和爱尔兰， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-adds-sixth-final-uk-tour-date-overwhelming-demand-3014951">“Hit Me Hard And Soft”巡演的这一部分包括在伦敦 O2 的六晚，</a>您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问这里获取任何剩余的北美门票</a>，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里获取英国/爱尔兰门票</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-for-cryin-out-loud-2025-uk-european-and-australian-tour-buy-tickets-3798210">Finneas 已确定 2025 年在新西兰、澳大利亚、英国、欧洲</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-for-cryin-out-loud-2025-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3800278">北美</a>举办个人演唱会。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-and-finneas-join-forces-for-wildflower-and-birds-of-a-feather-on-snl-3804392">《观看比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)》和芬尼斯 (Finneas) 在《周六夜现场》(SNL) 中联手演绎《野花》和《物以类聚》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME</a> 》上。</p> ;
利亚姆·佩恩去世后，One Direction 赢得了有史以来最大的流媒体日https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-earn-biggest-streaming-day-of-all-time-following-liam-paynes-death-3804388?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=one-继利亚姆·佩恩斯死亡之后，方向赚取最大的流媒体日Laura MolloySun, 20 Oct 2024 08:48:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3804388 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队的其余成员本周早些时候向佩恩表示敬意，称他们需要时间“哀悼并处理失去我们深爱的兄弟”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-earn-biggest-streaming-day-of-all-time-following-liam-paynes-death-3804388">利亚姆·佩恩去世后，《One Direction》的帖子创下了有史以来流媒体播放量最高的一天，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">Liam Payne</a>周三（10 月 16 日）去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>实现了迄今为止最大的流媒体日。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>佩恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落身亡，</a>年仅 31 岁。据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/oct/17/liam-payne-died-of-multiple-traumas-and-internal-and-external-bleeding" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道，阿根廷检察官办公室透露，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。</p><p> One Direction 的幸存成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zayn-malik">扎恩·马利克 (Zayn Malik)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niall-horan">尼尔·霍兰 (Niall Horan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-speak-out-on-the-death-of-liam-payne-were-completely-devastated-3803904">本周早些时候就佩恩的去世发表了一份联合声明，他们在声明中表达了悲痛，并表示他们需要时间“哀悼并处理失去我们兄弟的痛苦”。我们深爱着。”</a></p><p>自从佩恩不幸去世后，随着粉丝们追忆开启他职业生涯的歌曲，他的前乐队的音乐在流媒体排行榜上不断攀升。据<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBUfmzqTnDh/?igsh=OXA5azIwMmpqazJv&amp;img_index=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Complex</em></a>报道，10 月 17 日，他们的音乐在全球范围内获得了 5750 万次流媒体播放，这是他们迄今为止在流媒体平台上取得的最高数字。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/conormurray/2024/10/18/one-direction-hits-no-2-artist-on-global-spotify-chart-after-liam-paynes-death/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《福布斯》</em></a>报道，该男孩乐队目前是英国 Spotify 排名第一的艺人以及全球排名第二的艺人，仅次于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> )。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">利物浦利亚姆·佩恩守夜：哀悼者静静地唱着 One Direction 的《我一生的故事》 <a href="https://t.co/gzXC6az0m9">pic.twitter.com/gzXC6az0m9</a></p><p> - Con Corner (@ConCorner23) <a href="https://twitter.com/ConCorner23/status/1847634490908168607?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 19 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>该乐队 2014 年专辑《Four》中的热门单曲《Night Changes》一直是播放次数最多的歌曲之一，在 Spotify 每日全球歌曲排行榜上以超过 460 万次播放量上升至第六位，并成为 TikTok 热门歌曲中的第六位。</p><p>其他重新进入 Spotify 排行榜的歌曲包括“Story of My Life”、“What Makes You Beautiful”和“Perfect”。</p><p>此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-fans-hold-vigils-for-liam-payne-in-liverpool-3804346">，世界各地的球迷都在为佩恩守夜，其中包括利物浦</a>和他去世的阿根廷。本周早些时候，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-father-reads-fan-tributes-outside-argentinian-hotel-where-he-died-3804283">父亲杰夫加入了卡萨苏尔酒店外的人群</a>，感谢聚集在一起纪念他儿子的粉丝。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">在整个音乐界，其他人都向佩恩表示了敬意</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shawn-mendes-dedicates-heart-of-gold-to-liam-payne-3804271">肖恩·门德斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-maggie-rogers-pay-tribute-to-liam-payne-with-tender-cover-of-one-directions-night-changes-3804224">玛吉·罗杰斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-the-struggles-of-liam-payne-his-trials-and-tribulations-were-very-similar-to-mine-3804014">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rita-ora-performs-tearful-liam-payne-duet-hours-after-his-death-3803926">丽塔·奥拉</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-comments-on-liam-paynes-death-life-is-precious-3803700">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">维多利亚·卡纳尔</a>。</p><p>佩恩的前伴侣、佩恩 7 岁儿子贝尔的母亲<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cheryl-cole">谢丽尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cheryl-indescribably-painful-death-liam-payne-please-give-liam-little-dignity-he-has-left-3804228">公开讲述了这一“难以形容的痛苦”损失</a>，并敦促人们“给予利亚姆仅存的一点尊严”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-cassidy-girlfriend-of-liam-payne-pays-tribute-i-will-continue-to-love-you-for-the-rest-of-my-life-3804236">佩恩去世时的女友凯特·卡西迪也公开表示</a>：“我完全不知所措。过去几天的一切都感觉不到真实。我请求并祈祷你能给我恩典和空间来私下解决这个问题。”</p><p>其他消息方面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zayn-malik-postpones-us-tour-over-heartbreaking-loss-of-liam-payne-3804342">由于佩恩去世，马利克推迟了他的美国巡演</a>。这些演出将于一月份举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-earn-biggest-streaming-day-of-all-time-following-liam-paynes-death-3804388">利亚姆·佩恩去世后，《One Direction》的帖子创下了有史以来流媒体播放量最高的一天，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
